    ,('Knight Foundation','National Foundation For The Advancement In The Arts',200000.0,NULL,NULL,'donation log','Arts','https://knightfoundation.org/grants/6108',NULL,'Grant period: 09/01/2013 - 08/31/2014; goal: To launch the YoungArts Salon - a series of discussions with creative luminaries in the literary, visual and design arts; including an evening with Marina Abramovic and Matthu Placek, which will precede the Art Basel 2013 public premier of their collaborative work “A Portrait of Marina Abramovic” at the YoungArts Miami Campus.',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'YoungArts Salon')
