    ,('Knight Foundation','Submittable',0.0,NULL,NULL,'donation log','Technology, Journalism','https://knightfoundation.org/grants/4984',NULL,'Grant period: 02/05/2013 - Invalid date; goal: Submittable enables publishers to collect, review and charge for submissions of text, video and pictures, providing better, more timely responses to audience generated content. Here’s how it works: Once content arrives in the system, Submittable’s sorting, filtering, and ranking features make it easy to curate and take action on the incoming work. Multiple editors or readers can view, comment, and rank submissions. The software also helps publishers create value by putting a small charge - usually no more than what the post office charges to send a letter - on the submission process. This increase quality, decreases spam and creates revenue for the presently undervalued editorial skill sets.',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Submittable')
