    ,('Knight Foundation','Stroome',230000.0,NULL,NULL,'donation log','Technology','https://knightfoundation.org/grants/4733',NULL,'Grant period: 09/01/2010 - 08/31/2012; part of the challenge: Knight News Challenge; goal: To create a popular open source online collaborative video-editing platform To simplify the production of news video, Stroome will create a virtual video-editing studio. There, correspondents, editors and producers will be able to upload and share content, edit and remix with friends and colleagues – all without using expensive satellite truck technology. The site will launch as eyewitness video – often captured by mobile phones or web cams – is becoming a key component of news coverage, generating demand for supporting tools.',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Stroome')
