    ,('Knight Foundation','Teatro Avante',150000.0,NULL,NULL,'donation log','Communities, Arts','https://knightfoundation.org/grants/4569',NULL,'Grant period: 12/01/2009 - 10/31/2012; part of the challenge: Knight Arts Challenge; goal: To support and enhance an award-winning Hispanic theater festival by adding a comprehensive Latin American theater conference Teatro Avante will elevate the importance of Hispanic theater in Miami by expanding its 25th annual International Hispanic Theatre Festival in 2010. The educational component, co-sponsored by the Florida Center for the Literary Arts at Miami Dade College and Mexico’s Rodolfo Usigli Theatre Research Center, in collaboration with the Mexican Cultural Institute in Miami, will include a conference on Latin American theatre, post-performance forums, visual art and other exhibits.',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'International Hispanic Theatre Festival')
